{"tid":2369658,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Win 10一句指令可使硬碟損壞  或無法完全修復","createTime":"2021-01-17T10:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T06:36:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"75720bfdc41fdc854f3997da23c6fad5815762df","tid":2369658,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/17/windows-10-reproduces-bugs-and-damages-users-hard-drives/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F17%2Fwindows-10-reproduces-bugs-and-damages-users-hard-drives%2Flife-tech%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=f5d2cf46\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/17/windows-10-reproduces-bugs-and-damages-users-hard-drives/life-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然之前 Windows 10 亦出現過不少 Bug，不過多數影響小部分用戶。近日外國研究人員發現一個 Windows 10 Bug，只需使用一句短字串指令便可令用戶硬碟損壞，而從文中測試影片看來，似乎沒辦法完全修復。而最危險的是這個 Bug 似乎對所有 Windows 10 電腦都有影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/command.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fcommand.jpg&h=299a7536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/2-1-1079x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F2-1-1079x900.png&h=f5210d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/6-1077x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F6-1077x900.png&h=55b68922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/7-1077x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F7-1077x900.png&h=d2104261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/event-viewer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fevent-viewer.jpg&h=09a07b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日外國網站 Bleeping Computer 發佈文章並指出他們發現的一個 Windows 10 Bug。根據文章指出，只需一句簡單的短字串指令，使能夠破壞使用者 NTFS 格式硬碟。而且這個指令還可以使用多種方式來引導使用者觸發，例如偽裝成 ZIP、HTML 文件甚至是其他文件格式等。<br />\n<br />\n而從文章中的測試影片看來，似乎沒辦法完全修復。只要輸入該短字串指令後，雖然會顯示無法找到。但過了幾秒鐘之後，就會跳出需要重新啟動修復硬碟錯誤，並且要求現在重新開機。接著便會進入修復畫面，修復完後重新開機會再度出現錯誤，然後再次進行修復硬碟錯誤。而 Windows 10 事件日誌也出現錯誤報告。<br />\n<br />\n另外，這個 Bug 似乎對所有 Windows 10 電腦都有影響。因此只要有黑客在文件中加入此指令，而用戶不小心下載並執行便有可能導致硬碟損壞。目前並不知道這個短字串指令為何會導致硬碟損壞，不過有報導指出 Windows 10 其實早就有類似 Bug，研究人員亦有向 Microsoft 報告錯誤。"},{"pid":"25a466bacdbe6c35da23d9da747bd2aab4719d10","tid":2369658,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62620b315cdc383c8d6ba83c90ca99af2694a9e3","tid":2369658,"uid":156133,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"John Linux La"},{"pid":"a5d14182c671ee6f15a3c6f39a82cead428b4854","tid":2369658,"uid":30347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"渣 ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6099ed2055e631597defd3aa1e9bdd1a1f198e","tid":2369658,"uid":28528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5640b112f654ac764ef2e42f0571c528099b57","tid":2369658,"uid":88886,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"垃圾總有人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc0b6db3452d5fdd6ac8a831f08992121dc8a